title: Urban Meyer discusses building a winning culture & shares stories from his coaching days
itunes:title: Urban Meyer discusses building a winning culture & shares stories from his coaching days
description:
DJ and Bucky are back with a new episode. First, the pair talk to Urban Meyer, as he discusses how to build a winning culture and shares stories from his coaching days (1:24). Then, the guys react to Meyer's interview and give their takeaways from it (30:09). After that, DJ gives his updated rankings for the top college QB prospects, which he ranked before the college football season initially (37:54). Next, the duo briefly talk about a few big college matchups during this upcoming weekend (50:58). To wrap up the show, the pair answer fan questions, which were left in the reviews (52:03).
